The annex form include:
1. Client Registration Form
Purpose: To register new clients into the system.  
Fields: - ClientID  
        - Full Name  
        - Address  
        - Phone  
        - Email 
  
2. Loan Application Form
Purpose: To record loan requests and assign the responsible loan officer.  
Fields:  - LoanID  
         - ClientID  
         - OfficerID  
         - Loan Amount  
         - Interest Rate  
         - Duration  

3. Repayment Form
Purpose: To track repayment details for each loan.  
Fields: - RepaymentID  
        - LoanID  
        - Due Date  
        - Amount Paid  
        - Amount Due  
        - Status   

4. Savings Account Form
Purpose: To open and manage client savings accounts.  
Fields:  - SavingsID  
         - ClientID  
         - Account Number  
         - Open Date  
         - Balance  

5. Transaction Form
Purpose: To record deposits, withdrawals, and loan transactions.  
Fields:  - TransactionID  
         - Transaction Type  
         - Transaction Date  
         - Amount  
         - LoanID  
         - SavingsID  

6. Loan Officer Form
Purpose: To register and manage loan officers.  
Fields:  - OfficerID  
         - Full Name  
         - Phone Number  
         - Email  


